同城票据网助手，自动计算票据的贴现率，帮助您找到最佳票据。
使用说明：右键选项配置参数，设置票据的贴现率规则，打开https://www.tcpjw.com/B2BHall/ 进入企企大厅，系统自动计算渠道的贴现率。
long.en:
Tongcheng Bill Net Assistant automatically calculates the discount rate of bills to help you find the best bills.
Instructions for use: Quick option to configure parameters, set the discount rate rule of the bill, open https://www.tcpjw.com/B2BHall/ to enter the attempt hall, and the system automatically calculates the discount rate of the channel.
